            <!-- Problem 1 -->
            <div class="row align-items-center mb-5">
                <div class="col-md-6 fit-content">
                    <h3 class="problem__title">Undifferentiated value proposition</h3>
                    <p class="problem__description">When your positioning lacks clarity, potential customers can't articulate why they should choose you over competitors. This leads to commoditization, price sensitivity, and an inability to charge premium rates for your product.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="arrow"></div>
                <div class="col-md-6 solution-content">
                    <h4>Solution</h4>
                    <p class="solution__description">Our differentiation workshop identifies your unique value drivers and creates positioning that highlights your strengths. We develop clear, compelling messaging that communicates your distinct advantages, allowing you to command premium pricing.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Problem 2 -->
