            </div>
            <div class="faq-items">
                <!-- FAQ Item 1 -->
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question-wrapper">
                        <span class="faq-question">How long does a positioning project typically take?</span>
                        <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="faq-answer">Our standard positioning workshop takes 2 days, with preparation work requiring about 1-2 weeks. The complete positioning package typically spans 4-6 weeks from start to finish, depending on the complexity of your market and the depth of research required.</p>
                </div>
                <!-- FAQ Item 2 -->
                <div class="faq-item">
                     <div class="faq-question-wrapper">
                        <span class="faq-question">How is your positioning methodology different?</span>
                        <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="faq-answer">Unlike generic marketing agencies, we specialize exclusively in SaaS positioning. Our framework is based on extensive experience with 10+ SaaS companies and combines competitive analysis, customer research, and benefit mapping to create positioning that drives measurable business results.</p>
                </div>
                <!-- FAQ Item 3 -->
                 <div class="faq-item">
                     <div class="faq-question-wrapper">
                        <span class="faq-question">Do we need to have customer data before starting?</span>
                        <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="faq-answer">While customer data is valuable, it's not a prerequisite. Our process includes gathering insights through stakeholder interviews and market research. If you have existing customer feedback or analytics, we'll incorporate that data to strengthen your positioning strategy.</p>
                </div>
                <!-- FAQ Item 4 -->
                <div class="faq-item">
                     <div class="faq-question-wrapper">
                        <span class="faq-question">How do you measure positioning success?</span>
                        <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="faq-answer">We establish clear KPIs at the start of the project, typically including metrics like conversion rate improvements, sales cycle length reduction, win rate increases, and higher average deal values. We also track qualitative indicators like customer understanding of your value proposition.</p>
                </div>
                <!-- FAQ Item 5 -->
                 <div class="faq-item">
                     <div class="faq-question-wrapper">
                        <span class="faq-question">Can positioning help if we're in a crowded market?</span>
                        <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="faq-answer">Absolutely. In fact, clear positioning is even more critical in crowded markets. We'll help you identify underserved segments or unique value combinations that competitors have overlooked, allowing you to carve out a distinctive market position even in competitive landscapes.</p>
                </div>
                <!-- FAQ Item 6 -->
                 <div class="faq-item">
                     <div class="faq-question-wrapper">
                        <span class="faq-question">Should we reposition our product if it's already established?</span>
                        <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="faq-answer">Repositioning an established product can be powerful when entering new markets, facing new competitors, or when growth has plateaued. Our process includes careful evaluation of your current position and a strategic transition plan to minimize disruption while maximizing impact.</p>
                </div>
                <!-- FAQ Item 7 -->
                 <div class="faq-item">
                     <div class="faq-question-wrapper">
                        <span class="faq-question">Who from our team needs to be involved?</span>
                        <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="faq-answer">The most effective positioning workshops include leadership from product, marketing, and sales functions, plus the CEO for strategic alignment. We typically work with 4-6 key stakeholders who have deep understanding of your product, customers, and market dynamics.</p>
                </div>
                <!-- FAQ Item 8 -->
                 <div class="faq-item">
                     <div class="faq-question-wrapper">
                        <span class="faq-question">What deliverables will we receive?</span>
                        <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="faq-answer">Our standard deliverables include a comprehensive positioning statement, ideal customer profiles, competitive differentiation analysis, core value proposition, messaging framework, and implementation guidelines. The complete package also includes customer journey mapping and channel-specific messaging recommendations.</p>
                </div>
                <!-- FAQ Item 9 -->
                 <div class="faq-item">
                     <div class="faq-question-wrapper">
                        <span class="faq-question">How does positioning relate to our product roadmap?</span>
                        <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="faq-answer">Strong positioning should influence your product roadmap by highlighting the features and capabilities that reinforce your unique market position. We'll help you identify product enhancement opportunities that strengthen your competitive differentiation and resonate with your target audience.</p>
                </div>
                <!-- FAQ Item 10 -->
                 <div class="faq-item">
                     <div class="faq-question-wrapper">
                        <span class="faq-question">Do you help with implementation after the strategy is complete?</span>
                        <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="faq-answer">Yes, our complete positioning package includes implementation support to ensure your new positioning is effectively applied across your marketing channels, sales materials, and product experience. We also offer ongoing consulting to help your team navigate the positioning rollout and measure results.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

